QuestData.Title: Work Order: Operation: Shieldwall I
QuestData.Description: <Yoon's writing decorates the page though his feelings seem conflicted.>$b$bI normally try to stay out of conflict, but an order is an order. Since you are of the Alliance I decided to pass this order your way.$b$bOperation: Shieldwall has requested a whole heap of witchberries.$b$bI can't be sure, but I think they have an idea to use them in some sort of weapon.
QuestData.LogDescription: Plant 8 Witchberry Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
